00:16:02,400 --> 00:16:04,400
C is minus 1 half B.

285
00:16:04,400 --> 00:16:07,400
So what happens to this?

286
00:16:07,400 --> 00:16:10,400
This becomes B over 2,

287
00:16:11,400 --> 00:16:14,400
times x.

288
00:16:14,400 --> 00:16:16,400
And what happens to this one?

289
00:16:16,400 --> 00:16:25,400
This one becomes minus

290
00:16:25,400 --> 00:16:30,400
B over 2 times y.

291
00:16:30,400 --> 00:16:32,400
Still, we'll get the same magnetic field.

292
00:16:32,400 --> 00:16:37,400
This is a little exercise to prove that the magnetic field comes out exactly the same.

293
00:16:37,400 --> 00:16:40,400
Alright, so these are called gauge transformations.

294
00:16:40,400 --> 00:16:42,400
And a particular choice,

295
00:16:42,400 --> 00:16:45,400
